## Introduction

Keeping your system up to date usually involves invoking multiple package managers.
This results in big, non-portable shell one-liners saved in your shell.
To remedy this, **Topgrade** detects which tools you use and runs the appropriate commands to update them.

![Demo](http://rawcdn.githack.com/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/topgrade/img/topgrade_demo.gif "Demo")

## Usage

Just run `topgrade`.

## Configuration 

See `config.example.toml` for an example configuration file.
